name: user did not fill some of the checkout form element -- @1.5

steps.name: Given the user is logged in and has items in the cart
When the user proceeds to checkout from the cart page
Then the user should be on the checkout page
Then the user fill in the form "name" with ""
Then the user fill the "lastName" with "Doe"
Then The user fill the "zipcode" with "12345"
Then the user clicks on the continue button
Then the user should see an error message "Error: First Name is required"

fullName: Checkout Page functionality testing: user did not fill some of the checkout form element
